ActDepartment of Human Resources Development Act
Department of Employment and Social Development Act
PrecisAppointment of MARYANTONETT FLUMIAN of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development, to hold office during pleasure; to be concurrently an Associate Deputy Minister of Social Development, to hold office during pleasure; order that she shall be styled Deputy Minister for Service Canada; and appointment as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Vice-Chairperson of the Commission; effective October 5, 2005.
